Description: Danzo Retro Diaper Bag This very chic classic navy with red Danzo Retro Diaper Bag is perfect to stay organized on the go. Being a new parent, the last thing you need to worry about is leaving home without that extra diaper, change of clothes or even your money or keys. Introducing Danzo diaper bags. Not only are Danzo diaper bags stylish and trendy, they are uniquely designed with today's busy parents in mind. The bag conveniently zips down both side panels making easy access. Once inside, the real beauty of Danzo begins. Both sides of the bag are designed with a series of clear, easy to see through pockets. Each pocket is affixed with a velcro tab, to which a series of 25 different name tags can be attached.
